    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You make a (ranged) touch attack against the target. If it hits, the target is thrown back 1d6 x 5 ft if you used a melee touch attack or 1d4 x 5 ft if you made a ray attack. If the target collides with an object larger than it, it suffers 1d4 bludgeoning damage per 10 ft travelled, and falls @Condition[prone]{prone} in front of the object, not travelling further.</p>\n\n\n\n",
